title: 5/11/17 - The man who killed Osama, Rob O'Neill/Libertarian Party's Nicholas Sarwark
description:
Is President Trump alone in his own West Wing? ...30 officials inside the White House leaking information on Trump? ...Robert O'Neill, the Navy SEAL who shot Osama bin Laden joins Glenn in studio ...First hand accounts on the rescue attempts for Marcus Luttrell, Captain Phillips and the killing of Osama bin Laden ...Libertarian Party Chairman Nicholas Sarwark visits ...Why doesn't Glenn feel welcome in the Libertarian Party? ...How big of a missed opportunity was 2016 for the Libertarian Party? ...Is a third party going to be a real option going forward in American politics?

The Glenn Beck Program with Glenn Beck, Pat Gray, Stu Burguiere and Jeff Fisher, Weekdays 9a–12pm ET on TheBlaze Radio
